Class ActivityInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jcore.ControlNodeInstance
      • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jcore.ActivityInstance

  • public class ActivityInstance
extends ControlNodeInstance
    Represents the activity instance. It save the state of the activity in the state machine. It has an outgoing behavior and an incoming behavior.
